# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Lesson 15 -- Vision Inspect + Image Generation  [KEYLESS]
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# L15 is KEYLESS end to end -- there is NO key in this file. Auth flows
# through DefaultAzureCredential (az login); the signed-in user holds the
# "Cognitive Services OpenAI User" role on the Foundry resource. The SDK
# clients build a bearer token via get_bearer_token_provider -- no key is
# ever read.
#
# Two scripts share ONE Foundry resource and ONE endpoint:
#   lesson-15-vision-inspect.py  -> gpt-4o vision (image UNDERSTANDING / input)
#   lesson-15-contoso-promo.py   -> gpt-image-2  (image GENERATION / output)
#
# How to get these values:
#   1. Run Deploy-Lesson15-Infrastructure.ps1 (pass a unique -FoundryName).
#   2. Copy the printed output block here.
#   3. Never commit .env -- only .env.example.
#
#   AOAI_ENDPOINT:
#     The openai.azure.com endpoint the script reads. The deploy script prints
#     the ready-to-paste value (it rewrites the cognitiveservices form for you).
#     Example format: https://YOUR-RESOURCE-NAME.openai.azure.com/
#
#   AOAI_VISION_DEPLOYMENT:
#     Deployment name for the gpt-4o (vision-capable) chat model.
#     Default deploy creates this as "gpt-4o".
#
#   AOAI_IMAGE_DEPLOYMENT:
#     Deployment name for the gpt-image-2 model.
#     Default deploy creates this as "gpt-image-2".
#
#   AOAI_API_VERSION:
#     GA data-plane version for chat/vision calls (2024-10-21).
#
#   AOAI_IMAGE_API_VERSION:
#     PREVIEW data-plane version for image generation (2025-04-01-preview).
#     Image gen requires a separate preview version -- distinct from the GA
#     chat version above.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
AOAI_ENDPOINT=https://YOUR-RESOURCE-NAME.openai.azure.com/
AOAI_VISION_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-4o
AOAI_IMAGE_DEPLOYMENT=gpt-image-2
AOAI_API_VERSION=2024-10-21
AOAI_IMAGE_API_VERSION=2025-04-01-preview

# NEVER commit .env -- only .env.example.
